  delayBetweenMessages: 1
  lines:
  - ': Thought so, just always wanted to speak to you is all. '
  - "I\u2019m impressed how you were able to raise her so well alone, this is far
    from a place that rewards being a single parent, especially with the pay you
    get. "
  - "My sympathy, I couldn\u2019t imagine how hard that must be on all fronts."
  bridgeAfterMessages: 1
  bridgeResponse1: "I\u2019m hardly the reason she\u2019s been able to achieve all
    that she\u2019s done for herself, but thank you nonetheless."
